      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUNSET CLARICE (2) is yet to miss the placings in an excellent record this trip which boasts 10 wins and four placings. Scored by 1.5 lengths last time (27.52) in a OPEN over 488m at Mandurah. Looks the one to beat with even luck. SILENT ASSASSIN (1) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a 0.8 lengths third (30.11) behind Garritty at this track. Expected to feature. ASTON RULER (8) has a strong record here with 10 wins and seven placings from 25 starts. Below best last time at this track (30.46) in a Grade 5, finishing a 6 length eighth. Makes strong appeal on best. ASTON FREDDIE (7) scored with plenty to spare last time. Big chance on that form.",
